trans-unit.source: Specifies metadata for a type, property, field, or method marked with the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.ExportAttribute"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Angir metadataene for typen, egenskap, felt eller metode merket med den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.ExportAttribute"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.ExportMetadataAttribute"></xref> with the specified name and metadata value.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Composition.ExportMetadataAttribute"> </xref> med den angitte verdien for navn og metadata.

trans-unit.source: A string that contains the name of the metadata value, or <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> to set the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.ExportMetadataAttribute.Name*> property to an empty string ("").
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder navnet på metadataverdi eller <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> til å angi den <xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.ExportMetadataAttribute.Name*>egenskapen til en tom streng ("").</xref:System.ComponentModel.Composition.ExportMetadataAttribute.Name*>

trans-unit.source: An object that contains the metadata value.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som inneholder verdien metadata.

trans-unit.source: This can be <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Dette kan være <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets or sets a value that indicates whether this item is marked with this attribute more than once.
trans-unit.target: Henter eller angir en verdi som angir om elementet er merket mer enn én gang med attributtet.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the item is marked more than once; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis elementet er merket flere ganger; Ellers <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the name of the metadata value.
A string that contains the name of the metadata value.
trans-unit.target: En streng som inneholder navnet på verdien metadata.

trans-unit.source: An object that contains the metadata value.
trans-unit.target: Et objekt som inneholder verdien metadata.
